# claim prop 的意义是，如果prop的参数列表里面的参数数量大于涉及到的specFact的参数数量，那为了让未来能对应上，要给这个forall取个名字，即claim prop

prove:
    prop p(x R)
    prop q(x R)
    prop t(x R)

    know forall x R: $p(x) => $q(x)
    know forall x R: $q(x) => $t(x)

    prop p_to_t(x R):
        $p(x)

    claim:
        forall x R:
            $p(x)
            =>:
                $t(x)
        prove:
            $q(x)
            $t(x)

